<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν Πεττυκᾶμις ὁ κεραμεὺς ἀφ᾽ Ἱερᾶς Νήσου. πεῖραν <choice><corr>μέν</corr><sic>μεμ</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="2"/>μου εἴληφας εἴτε εἰμὶ τεχνίτης εἴτε καὶ οὔ. ἵνα οὖν, εἰ μέλλω ἐργάζεσθαι, 

    <lb n="3"/>ἀναγκαῖόν με τοὺς τεχνίτας τοὺς μέλλοντάς μοι εἶναι χρησίμους κατίσχειν 

    <lb n="4"/>μετ᾽ ἐμαυτοῦ. προσπαραλήψομαι δὲ καὶ Παῆσιν καὶ τοὺς υἱοὺς αὐτοῦ· 

    <lb n="5"/>δοκιμάζω γὰρ αὐτούς, ἅμα δὲ καὶ τῆς γῆς τῆς ἐνταῦθα οὐκ <choice><corr>ἄπειροί</corr><sic>απιροι</sic></choice> εἰσιν. 

    <lb n="6"/>ὥρα δέ ἐστιν ἐργάζεσθαι ἀπὸ τοῦ Θῶυθ, ἵνα τὰ ἔργα χωρίς τε συντελεσ-

    <lb n="7"/>θῇ ἐν ὥραι καὶ ἅμα χρήσιμα.  εὐτύχει. 

    <lb n="8"/>καὶ τὸν τόπον <choice><corr>κέλευσόν</corr><sic>κελευσομ</sic></choice> μοι παραδεῖξαι ἐν ὧι ἐργῶμαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.1138" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1138" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="-275" notAfter="-226">Mitte III v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1138" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Datierung nach dem Rahmen des Zenon - Archivs.</p></div><div n="meta.1138" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.1138" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59500</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">1138</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59500</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0092;3;59500" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1138" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Pl. XXIV</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1138" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de" default="NO"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Mees, Organisationsformen römischer Töpfer-Manufakturen (2002), S. 367</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1138" type="history" subtype